ot;html\&quot;:\&quot;\u003cp\u003eWelcome to the \u003cstrong\u003eOL Conn=
ect\\u003C/strong\u003e user forums. This space is provided by Upland Objec=
tif Lune for the OL Connect user community to ask questions, make suggestio=
ns and share information about the application in order to get the most out=
 of it!\\u003C/p\u003e\\n\u003cp\u003eNote that the forums for the classic =
products PlanetPress Suite, PrintShop Mail Suite and PReS are now in read-o=
nly mode but can still be accessed for reference \u003ca href=3D\\\&quot;ht=
tp://newsgroup.objectiflune.com/forum2/ubbthreads.php?ubb=3Dpostlist\u0026a=
mp;Board=3D84\\\&quot;\u003ehere\\u003C/a\u003e.\\u003C/p\u003e\\n\u003cp\u=
003eBefore asking a question that may already have been addressed here or e=
lsewhere, make sure to check out the following sources before posting:\\u00=
3C/p\u003e\\n\u003cul\u003e\\n\u003cli\u003eCheck out the the \u003ca href=
=3D\\\&quot;https://help.uplandsoftware.com/objectiflune\\\&quot;\u003eonli=
ne help\\u003C/a\u003e\\u003C/li\u003e\\n\u003cli\u003eTake a look at the \=
u003ca href=3D\\\&quot;https://olresourcecenter.uplandsoftware.com/\\\&quot=
;\u003eResource Center\\u003C/a\u003e, which offers resources, libraries, s=
ample files and tutorials.\\u003C/li\u003e\\n\u003cli\u003eSearch these for=
ums to see if the question was answered previously.\\u003C/li\u003e\\n\\u00=
3C/ul\u003e\\n\u003cp\u003eAlso, here are a few small guidelines for postin=
g on these forums:\\u003C/p\u003e\\n\u003cul\u003e\\n\u003cli\u003ePlease b=
e as descriptive as possible in your post and provide all the relevant info=
rmation.\\u003C/li\u003e\\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNever post any p=
ersonal or confidential content on this forum\\u003C/strong\u003e - it is a=
ccessible by anyone and is not secure (same goes for links to files on othe=
r servers).\\u003C/li\u003e\\n\u003cli\u003eKeep it civil and try to \u003c=
a href=3D\\\&quot;http://www.albion.com/netiquette/introduction.html\\\&quo=
t;\u003efollow the netiquette\\u003C/a\u003e. We are all human with emotion=
s, but solutions are rarely achieved when those emotions are high.\\u003C/l=
i\u003e\\n\u003cli\u003eSpam, violence, racism, personal insults and other =
unwanted behaviours will be dealt with swiftly.\\u003C/li\u003e\\n\u003cli\=
u003eThere are no robots, automated messages, or canned responses in these =
forums. Every answer is typed by a human. That is, as far as we know=E2=80=
=A6 The point is, humans can sometimes make mistakes, so be lenient.\\u003C=
/li\u003e\\n\u003cli\u003eAnd above all, please enjoy your time here, don=
=E2=80=99t be afraid to ask anything and participate if you want to lend a =
hand.\\u003C/li\u003e\\n\\u003C/ul\u003e\\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eN=
ote\\u003C/strong\u003e : Posts are not guaranteed to be answered within an=
y specific time frame and may not offer you any definitive answer depending=
 on the complexity of your issue. Remember that if you have a \u003cstrong\=
u003evalid OL Care contract\\u003C/strong\u003e, you can \u003ca href=3D\\\=
&quot;https://olresourcecenter.uplandsoftware.com/\\\&quot;\u003econtact ou=
r technical support department\\u003C/a\u003e directly.\\u003C/p\u003e\&quo=
