            <div id=3D"banner-content"><p>Welcome to the <strong>OL Connect=
</strong> user forums. This space is provided by Upland Objectif Lune for t=
he OL Connect user community to ask questions, make suggestions and share i=
nformation about the application in order to get the most out of it!</p>
<p>Note that the forums for the classic products PlanetPress Suite, PrintSh=
op Mail Suite and PReS are now in read-only mode but can still be accessed =
for reference <a href=3D"http://newsgroup.objectiflune.com/forum2/ubbthread=
s.php?ubb=3Dpostlist&amp;Board=3D84">here</a>.</p>
<p>Before asking a question that may already have been addressed here or el=
sewhere, make sure to check out the following sources before posting:</p>
<ul>
<li>Check out the the <a href=3D"https://help.uplandsoftware.com/objectiflu=
ne">online help</a></li>
<li>Take a look at the <a href=3D"https://olresourcecenter.uplandsoftware.c=
om/">Resource Center</a>, which offers resources, libraries, sample files a=
nd tutorials.</li>
<li>Search these forums to see if the question was answered previously.</li=
>
</ul>
<p>Also, here are a few small guidelines for posting on these forums:</p>
<ul>
<li>Please be as descriptive as possible in your post and provide all the r=
elevant information.</li>
<li><strong>Never post any personal or confidential content on this forum</=
strong> - it is accessible by anyone and is not secure (same goes for links=
 to files on other servers).</li>
<li>Keep it civil and try to <a href=3D"http://www.albion.com/netiquette/in=
troduction.html">follow the netiquette</a>. We are all human with emotions,=
 but solutions are rarely achieved when those emotions are high.</li>
<li>Spam, violence, racism, personal insults and other unwanted behaviours =
will be dealt with swiftly.</li>
<li>There are no robots, automated messages, or canned responses in these f=
orums. Every answer is typed by a human. That is, as far as we know=E2=80=
=A6 The point is, humans can sometimes make mistakes, so be lenient.</li>
<li>And above all, please enjoy your time here, don=E2=80=99t be afraid to =
ask anything and participate if you want to lend a hand.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Note</strong> : Posts are not guaranteed to be answered within a=
ny specific time frame and may not offer you any definitive answer dependin=
g on the complexity of your issue. Remember that if you have a <strong>vali=
d OL Care contract</strong>, you can <a href=3D"https://olresourcecenter.up=
landsoftware.com/">contact our technical support department</a> directly.</=
p></div><!---->
